---
group_count: 17
atr1_unknown: 0
entries:
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk000:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 284
      - text: "你这沃伊还真是了不起啊。\n肯定能更为熟练地使用乌尔波扎的愤怒了。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk010:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 273
      - text: "小公主她……就托付给你了。\n你可是我们海拉鲁引以为傲的勇者啊。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk100:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 216
      - text: "你的本领还是那么高超。\n看来海拉鲁的勇者威风不减当年啊。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk110:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 284
      - text: "不过，你可不要大意。\n你我应该都不愿再见到小公主哭泣吧。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk200:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 153
      - text: "我看到了。\n你的刀法十分娴熟。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk210:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 234
      - text: "对了，你去过格鲁德小镇了吧？\n现在谁是那里的族长？"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk220:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 246
      - text: "100年前，在我发生那样的事后……\n大家应该过得都很艰难吧。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk230:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 336
      - text: "但我相信……格鲁德是一个强大的民族。\n不管是怎样的灾难，我们都能勇敢面对！"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk300:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 177
      - text: "你又来了吗？\n现在的你已经没问题了。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk310:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 146
      - text: 另外，我想问你一件事……
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk320:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 186
      - text: "你去格鲁德小镇时，\n是怎样进入镇子的？"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk330:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 232
      - text: 难道……你又装扮成那副模样了？
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk340:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 241
      - text: "早在100年前，那装扮就很适合你了。\n好想让小公主也看看你那扮相啊。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk400:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 195
      - text: "刚才的一切我都看到了。\n我已经没有什么可以指导你了。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk410:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 206
      - text: "啊，对了。\n如果你今后在别处找到了我的日记……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk420:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 230
      - text: "就把它拿给小公主看吧。\n那上面写有我的朋友……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk430:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 332
      - text: "也就是她母亲的事情。\n她母亲去世得早，留下女儿与父亲相依为命。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk440:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 112
      - text: 想必她母亲也非常不舍吧……
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk500:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 246
      - text: "我拜托了你不少事情呢。\n像小公主的事情，还有海拉鲁的事情……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk510:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 264
      - text: "不过你一定能够完成的……\n因为你可是我认识的最出色的沃伊啊。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk520:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 220
      - text: "等到今后打倒了盖侬……\n我会亲自去和她母亲……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk530:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 101
      - text: 说小公主的事情……
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk540:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 262
      - text: "我会告诉她，“你女儿身边有一位\n出色的骑士，所以不用担心”。"
